   26      Return the list [G0,G1,...,G1252] of graphs as named in the Graph Atlas. 
   27      G0,G1,...,G1252 are all graphs with up to 7 nodes. 
   28

   30        1. in increasing order of number of nodes; 
   31        2. for a fixed number of nodes,
